	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I agree. Hey, perhaps when you register, state something like this:
<br />
<br />Do not post anything as your personal website until 7 days after you register. If you do, you will be banned.
<br />
<br />Would this be hard to stick in? If not, why not do it? This will give you the opportunity to look a the "New Members" list, and see who has a link to a website. If they do, cut them out. Even if not all spammers have a link, it still would heavily reduce the number here.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
